TASK
The task is to create an QUIZ API for weekly team bonnding fun. 

FRAMWORK FOR API - Laravel or NodeJs

There are two APIs
1. getQuestion API 
    A.  Input Age Range - Age 5-7, Age 8-12 and Age 13-15
    B. Output : 8 questions for selected AGE RANGE  from the question bank (2 questions randomly drawn from each section - Brain teasers, Ani,als, Childhood, Geography)
2. scoreQuiz API
    1.  Answers to each of the 8 questions for the Age range
    2. Mark quiz
    3. Response - questions correct and wrong with score /8


QUESTION BANK CATEGORIES (You only need 15 questions from each category. 5 questions for Age 5-7, Age 8-12 and Age 13-15)):
1. Brain teasers - https://github.com/uberspot/OpenTriviaQA/blob/master/categories/brain-teasers
2. Childhood - https://github.com/uberspot/OpenTriviaQA/blob/master/categories/for-kids
3. Animals - https://github.com/uberspot/OpenTriviaQA/blob/master/categories/animals
4. Geography - https://github.com/uberspot/OpenTriviaQA/blob/master/categories/geography


Inspiration: https://trivia.willfry.co.uk/

Deadline: It is expected that the task is completed within 3-4 hours
Respond to this email within 24 hours with the link to your task
